FOOTBALL: Hornets finish 9-0 in regular season The Argus-Press The Argus-Press | 0 comments 
MONTROSE — New Lothrop completed a 9-0 regular season by shutting out Montrose 41-0 Friday night. 
New Lothrop, posting its fourth shutout of the season, outgained the Rams 484-81 and it was the Hornets’ sixth consecutive unbeaten regular season.
